Create a descriptive well formatted cheatsheet for all the things you should know about Flexbox

Flex Box is based on CSS and it consists of 2 element types namely Container and items.

Quick start steps for FlexBox usage:
====================================

1.To start using Flexbox first step is to create a flex container.

.flex-container {
    display: flex;
}

/* OR */

.flex-container {
    display: inline-flex;
}

2. Once container is ready different properties can be applied to it. list of properties include:

    flex-direction
    flex-wrap
    flex-flow
    justify-content
    align-items
    align-content
    order
    align-self
    flex-grow
    flex-shrink
    flex-basis
    flex